title: SpeedUpMyPC 4.2.3.6 +serial -TrT
description:
SpeedUpMyPC 4.2.3.6
Full version with Serial

SpeedUpMyPC - the program is a handy tuner to your operating system and provides 
for its more stable and faster work. The program allows you to free memory and 
other system resources, to prevent fatal crashes, to reduce download time and 
make more effective communication with the Internet. The utility also allows 
you to monitor the system and makes recommendations to speed up the startup programs.

SpeedUpMyPC gives the ability to monitor and manage all the resources of a 
computer with one simple click. System settings, internet usage, disk clutter, 
RAM and CPU, everything will be automatically scanned, cleaned and optimized 
for maximum productivity. You can also pause or delete the background and 
process startup, to produce high-quality disk defragmentation and multipass 
grinding, for compliance with privacy, completely remove sensitive data and much more. 

Features: 
- Automatic scanning system performance 
- Overview of CPU 
- Improving the functionality of the processor 
- Review the use of RAM 
- Optimize RAM 
- Review the use of disk space 
- Analyzing and defragmenting hard drives 
- Analysis and optimization of the speed of Internet connections 
- Startup Manager 
- Task Manager 
- System Overview and recommendations for increasing its productivity 
- Crawling on unnecessary or unwanted data 
- Complete destruction of confidential data (optional) 
- Manager to uninstall the program 
- Nice and easy interface yuzersky 
- Run program at startup (optional) 
- Automatically start scanning the system at boot program (optional) 
- Run, program icon in system tray

INSTALL NOTES:

1) Unpack rar archive
2) Run speedupmypc.exe
3) Register program with serial (see serial.txt)
Done
